headline: The Los Angeles Sports & Entertainment Commission (LASEC) Names Amgen as Official Biotech Partner and Los Angeles World Cup 2026 Host City Supporter Ahead of FIFA World Cup 2026™
summary: The Los Angeles Sports & Entertainment Commission (LASEC), which serves as the lead for the Los Angeles World Cup 2026 Host Committee, today announced that Amgen, a leading biotechnology company headquartered in Greater Los Angeles, has been named a Foundational Partner and the Official Biotech Partner of LASEC. Amgen will also become an Official Los Angeles World Cup 2026 Host City Supporter.
